SixtyFourRoles
==============

User roles wich stored in integer field.

0. Installation

./script/plugin install git://github.com/oktoberliner/64roles.git

1. Mirgation

add_column :users, :role, :integer, :default => 0

2. User class

# realy important: append new roles only to end of roles list
class User
  has_roles :user, :admin
end

3. Usage

@user.admin? #=> false
@user.user? #=> false

@user.user = @user.admin = true

@user.admin? #=> true
@user.user? #=> true

@user.admin = false
@user.admin? #=> false

4. Get role by string

User.roles #=> [:user, :admin]

@user.is? :admin
@user.add_role :admin
@user.remove_role :user

5. I privet, tchyo